# Solution(Iteration)

```java
class Solution {
    public List<Integer> postorder(Node root) {
        List<Integer> res = new LinkedList<>();
        Stack<Node> s = new Stack<>();
        if(root!=null)s.push(root);
        while(!s.isEmpty()){
            Node node=s.peek();
            if(node!=null){
                s.pop();
                s.push(node);
                s.push(null);
                for (int i = node.children.size()-1; i >= 0; i--) {
                    s.push(node.children.get(i));
                }    
            }else{
                s.pop();
                node=s.pop();
                res.add(node.val);
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*
- space:*O(n)*

