# Solution(Iteration)

```java
class Solution {
    public List<Integer> preorderTraversal(TreeNode root) {
        List<Integer> res = new LinkedList<>();
        Stack<TreeNode> s = new Stack<>();
        if(root!=null)s.push(root);
        while(!s.isEmpty()){
            TreeNode node=s.peek();
            if(node!=null){
                s.pop();
                if(node.right!=null){
                    s.push(node.right);
                }
                if(node.left!=null){
                    s.push(node.left);
                }
                s.push(node);
                s.push(null);
            }else{
                s.pop();
                node=s.pop();
                res.add(node.val);
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*
- space:*O(n)*

