# Solution

```java
class Solution {
    public int magicTower(int[] nums) {
        int cnt=0;
        long sum=1,delay=0;
        Queue<Integer> heap=new PriorityQueue<>() ;
        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if(nums[i]<0){
                heap.offer(nums[i]);
            }
            sum+=nums[i];
            if(sum<=0){
                cnt++;
                int cur=heap.poll();
                delay+=cur;
                sum-=cur;// sumÂáèÊéâÊ≠§ÂâçÂä†ËøáÁöÑÊúÄÂ∞èË¥üÊï∞
            }
        }
        sum+=delay; // ÊúÄÂêé‰∏Ä‰∏™Êï∞Âà´Êó†ÈÄâÊã©
        return sum>0?cnt:-1;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*
- space:*O(n)*

