```java
class Solution {
    public int alternatingSubarray(int[] nums) {
        int max=1,flag=1,len=1;
        for (int i = 1; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if(nums[i]-nums[i-1]==flag){
                len++;
                flag*=-1;
            }else if(nums[i]-nums[i-1]==1){
                len=2;
                flag=-1;
            }else{
                len=1;
                flag=1;
            }
            max=Math.max(max,len);
        }
        return max==1?-1:max;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*
- space:*O(1)*

