class Solution {
    public int findBottomLeftValue(TreeNode root) {
        Queue<TreeNode> queue=new LinkedList<>();
        queue.offer(root);
        int res=root.val;
        while (!queue.isEmpty()){
            int size=queue.size();
            res=queue.peek().val;
            while (size-->0){
                TreeNode node=queue.poll();
                if(node.left!=null){
                    queue.offer(node.left);
                }
                if(node.right!=null){
                    queue.offer(node.right);
                }
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}
```

- time:*O(n)*
- space:*O(n)*

